## v136-v137 Network-Distance Scoring + Retreat Margin
- User modified targeting.py: replaced hub-centric penalty with network-distance
  - Uses min distance to ANY hub or friendly junction (enables chaining)
  - Expansion weight: 10.0 (cap 60), network penalty: dist * 0.5
- v136 8-cog (7 non-wipeout seeds): avg 3.85 — slight regression from hub-centric
- v137: increased retreat margin 15→20 to reduce deaths
- v137 8-cog (14 non-wipeout seeds): avg **5.12** — BEST EVER!
  - Seed 5: 13.24 (ABOVE TARGET!), seed 6: 6.72 (1 death!)
  - Seeds 10-17: no wipeouts, avg 5.04
- v137 breakthrough: network-distance + safety margin = fewer deaths + better expansion
